<p>Welcome to GreenLink, a tool to facilitate an exchange of environmental information. We offer few 
graphics allowing you to connect quickly to relevant information.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.greenlink.org/signup.html">Sign up</a> for a <b><blink>FREE</blink></b> Charter Membership in GreenLink and have access to:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.greenlink.org/current.html">GreenCurrents</a>, current hot environmental issues. </li>
<li><a href="http://www.greenlink.org/forum/index.html">GreenForums </a>, and our Rapid Response Network.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.greenlink.org/host.html">GreenLink Hosted Home Pages </a>, Environmental Organizations</li>
<li><a href="http://www.greenlink.org/data/index.html">Green Data </a>, data bases for environmental research</li>
<li><a href="http://www.greenlink.org/links.html">Other Environmental Links </a>on the World Wide Web </li>
<li><a href="http://www.greenlink.org/guides.html">GreenGuides </a>, a Who's Who of legislatures, agencies, and grass roots organizations.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.greenlink.org/watch.html">GreenWatch </a>, an eye on legislation affecting the environment (under construction).</li>
<li><a href="http://www.greenlink.org/news.html">GreenNews </a>, news from DC and around the country (under construction)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.greenlink.org/services.html">Other Services </a>, including special internet mail services for Greenlink members. </li>
<li><a href="http://www.greenlink.org/groups/index.html">GreenGroups</a> , grassroots environmental groups in Ohio</li>
<li><a href="http://www.greenlink.org/statbot/ps.html">Statistics </a>about our visitors. <a href="http://www.greenlink.org/graph1.gif">Graph of traffic last week</a> and <a href="http://www.greenlink.org/graph2.gif">last 24 hours</a>. </li>
</ul>
<p>Notice of Position: GEC is looking for an information resources librarian with internet experience. 
Please send resume.</p>
<p>Send <a href="mailto:gec@greenlink.org">E-mail</a> to the <a href="http://www.greenlink.org/gec/index.html">Greene Environmental Coalition </a>, our sponsor. </p>
