<p><i>AFFINITY </i>is Ohio's Free environmental newspaper
distributed throughout Northeastern Ohio and in various cities
and towns throughout the state. The purpose of this publication
is to provide vital information to help educate citizens so that
they can take a more active role in protecting their environment.
In addition <i>AFFINITY</i> serves as a forum for environmental
activists to voice their concerns.</p>

