<body bgcolor="#B1CFC8">
<h1>GreenNews</h1>
<hr>
<p><img src="/gif/undercons.gif" alt="Under Construction." align=top></p>
<p>Governor declares September 16-22 as Pollution Prevention Week. Governor Voinovich 
encourages all Ohioans to reduce waste, prevent pollution and expand markets for recycled goods.</p>
<p>More than 160 companies have become involved in pollution prevention through Ohio Prevention 
First which is a voluntary planning initiative that seeks to reduce the amount of pollution generated 
throughout Ohio by 50 percent by the year 2000.</p>
<p>Ohioans are urged to reduce and recylce, shop wisely and extend product lifespans, buy locally 
and organic, compost, save energy</p>
<p>This page is under construction, please drop in again to see the finished product. </p>
