<html>

<head>
<title>Good News in the Midwest</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#B1CFC8">
<h2>Good News in the Midwest</h2>
<p>&#160; </p>
<p>Governor Voinovich declares September 16-22 as Pollution Prevention Week. Governor 
Voinovich encourages all Ohioans to reduce waste, prevent pollution and expand markets for 
recycled goods.</p>
<p>More than 160 companies have become involved in pollution prevention through Ohio Prevention 
First which is a voluntary planning initiative that seeks to reduce the amount of pollution generated 
throughout Ohio by 50 percent by the year 2000.</p>
<p>Ohioans are urged to reduce and recycle, shop wisely and extend product lifespans, buy locally 
and organic, compost, save energy, plan ahead and pool resources, and avoid toxics.</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
</body>

