<p><a href="#JCARR Documents">JCARR Documents </a></p>
<hr>
<p>These pages are presented in Adobe Portable Document Format (PDF). You must have Adobe 
Reader installed on your computer to view these documents. Download the free Adobe Reader, 
<a href="ftp://ftp.greenlink.org/public-ftp/adobe/acroread.mac">Macintosh Version </a>(2.6 Mbytes),<a href="ftp://ftp.greenlink.org/public-ftp/adobe/acroread.exe"> Windows Version </a>(1.5 Mbytes) from our server. For other 
operating systems download software for free direct from Adobe at <a href="http://www.adobe.com/acrobat/readstep.html">www.adobe.com</a>. With Adobe 
reader you can print or view the documents in their original form. You may use the document just as 
if we mailed you a photocopy.</p>
<p>After installing the Adobe Reader, you will be able to view and print the downloaded files.</p>
<p>Remember Adobe PDF files are images, equivalent to photocopies of the original documents. It 
may take a few moments to download. </p>
