<h1 align=center>Ohio Brownfields Rules Proposed on 
October 3, 1996</h1>
<h3 align=left>All documents on these pages were scanned from originals supplied 
by OEPA as part of their public participation outreach. These 
documents reached our office less than one week prior to close of 
the public comment period. Please note that these Rule changes do 
not seem to include comments from the most recent round of public 
hearings. </h3>
