<DOCHDR>
http://www.greenlink.org:80/forum/REG-AGENCIES/00006/index.html 206.86.202.14 19970119094317 text/html 7837
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 19 Jan 1997 10:11:00 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
Content-type: text/html
