<html>

<head>
<title>TRI - TV show</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body>
<p>From: Paul Orum &lt;orump@RTK.NET </p>
<p>To: Right-to-Know Advocates</p>
<p>From: Paul Orum, Working Group on Comm. Right-to-Know</p>
