<h3 align=center>RIVER ALLIANCE OF WISCONSIN WEB PAGE UP AND 
RUNNING--</h3>
<h3 align=center><a href="http://www.igc.org/wisrivers">http://www.igc.org/wisrivers</a></h3>
<p>In addition to providing information on river issues in Wisconsin our page provides useful 
information on river fun in Wisconsin. It includes links for paddling information (put-ins, take-outs, 
info on individual rivers), fishing info (10 best rivers info, fly-tying, and links to fishing calendar of 
events), outfitters, weather and camping. </p>
<p>Check out our page for the most up-to-date information on the Crandon mine, dam removal and 
hydropower issues. We also have short segments from our newsletters on Stillwater Bridge, 
Mounds Dam, Watershed Organizing and many more. </p>
<p>One of the most complete water links pages anywhere. We have linked to many of you. If we don't 
have you mentioned on the page and you want a link please e-mail Zev at <a href="mailto:wisrivers@igc.apc.org">wisrivers@igc.apc.org</a> or 
call (608) 257-2424 </p>
