http://www.greenlink.org:80/affinity/120196/pcb.html 206.86.202.14 19970119095514 text/html 14882
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 19 Jan 1997 10:23:17 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 14710
Last-modified: Mon, 02 Dec 1996 15:22:02 GMT
